  <description type="morphology">Plants 40–70 cm. Stems yellowish green, usually leafless at flowering, compactly tomentose. Leaves yellowish green; blades 1-nerved, filiform, 10–30 × 0.7–1 mm, faces compactly tomentose. Involucres 9.5–12 mm. Phyllaries 22–25, apices erect, acute, abaxial faces tomentose or glabrate. Corollas 7–8.5 mm, tubes hairy, lobes 0.7–0.9 mm, villous; style appendages longer than stigmatic portions. Cypselae hairy; pappi 5.6–7.6 mm. 2n = 18.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering late summer-fall.</description>
